CHAPTER VI
FINANCING OF THE PROGRAMMES OF TECHNICAL COOPERATION IN OLIVE CULTIVATION , OLIVE-OIL EXTRACTION AND TABLE-OLIVE PROCESSING
Article 18
Sources of finance and administration
